beer.beer_description:
A dry and slightly funky Saison. 
25kgs of white wine grapes added to the mash add a delightful tart finish with hints of melon.
Lemondrop hops add some slight citrus notes.
A few typical Saison phenolic notes of banana and cloves on the nose and palate.
Well balanced and quite well rounded.
An all day thirst quencher.
